    "description": "<strong>Paper Needs Inspiration!</strong> is a survival resource management game where you play as Paper, a writer who needs new ideas for his work. To help Paper find his muse, the player must explore the world and find his reason for being there, thereby discovering a fresh artistic direction for his writings.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/f1110d84316f69f79f16f2516caba375.avif?t=1673118497\" width=616 height=234 /></span><br>Collecting resources in the world is an essential part of your journey. Learn to craft tools, then use them to farm the items that will help you in your journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/120c0c40965d065e90f498b30ab6ca08.poster.avif?t=1673118497\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/120c0c40965d065e90f498b30ab6ca08.webm?t=1673118497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/120c0c40965d065e90f498b30ab6ca08.mp4?t=1673118497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are many useful objects and structures to learn and build. They will help you survive the world as well as aid you in your progress towards finding your inspiration.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/25cab882a59a9274bfb2ac597623f3a2.poster.avif?t=1673118497\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/25cab882a59a9274bfb2ac597623f3a2.webm?t=1673118497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/25cab882a59a9274bfb2ac597623f3a2.mp4?t=1673118497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/364602cc8f783aa5c74f4bade2b2fa7a.avif?t=1673118497\" width=616 height=234 /></span><br>The world is procedurally generated and goes on forever and ever, with many unexpected things to encounter, so choose a direction and go exploring!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/a10e7277683fe2a9412e964091d33c2b.poster.avif?t=1673118497\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/a10e7277683fe2a9412e964091d33c2b.webm?t=1673118497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/a10e7277683fe2a9412e964091d33c2b.mp4?t=1673118497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Some animals you meet just won’t like you. That’s the time to put up a fight and show them who is in charge!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/57978cbd6d04b87036f2b43b90c6e60f.poster.avif?t=1673118497\" width=616 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/57978cbd6d04b87036f2b43b90c6e60f.webm?t=1673118497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/57978cbd6d04b87036f2b43b90c6e60f.mp4?t=1673118497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/51d69b2fdf6f7354e6f61b297a74f992.avif?t=1673118497\" width=616 height=234 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Brilliant HD visual presentation and sound<br></li><li>Abstract and bizarre beings to meet<br></li><li>Engage in interesting activities to survive<br></li><li>Dozens of items to learn and construct<br></li><li>Procedurally generated terrain, explore it forever<br></li><li>Unique hub worlds to visit<br></li><li>Existential main story</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206440/extras/de32509e1349bc37eac2d671a89eeedc.avif?t=1673118497\" width=616 height=234 /></span>",
